# Seccomp template

The included seccomp template (seccomp-template.json):
  - Blocks all syscalls except a small safe allowlist
  - Allows Python to run, allocate memory, read/write files, and exit
  - Blocks networking, mounting, ptrace, kernel modules, etc.


Enable it with

    docker run --security-opt seccomp=docs/seccomp-template.json ...
